title: New Kids On the Block ( Coi Leray Interview)
itunes:title: New Kids On the Block ( Coi Leray Interview)
description:
Today on the show we Coi Leray stop by for the first time, who spoke about the new generation, of music, Nicki Minaj Collab, her father Benzino, feeling pressured and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the Tennessee law makers for eliminating age requirements for marriages, which would be opening the doors to major society issues. Next, we had Cassandra Cummings stop by who spoke about stocks & stilettos society, empowering black women to invest and more.
